metadata.name: The Path — Parc de Sceaux
metadata.description:
Collage made from an analog photograph of a pathway in Parc de Sceaux repeated 8 times.
—
This artwork is part of Swinging Gardens, a digital extension of the exhibition LE JARDIN QUI BASCULE, presented at Galerie C from April 18th to June 3rd, 2023 in Paris.
